Create a run director <rundir>
mkdir <rundir>
cd <rundir>
source $MC/bin/setup.csh
(if you are in csh or tcsh
For bash Angelos will write the correct setup file)
You end up inside the a src directory.
Now choose a config file from the $MC/config directory
Then run:
ln -s $MC/config/config.dmdesk config.local
If you want to test the calculation of derivatives:
make der_test
mv der_test ../
cd ..
./der_test.exe
